N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 101.1 - Establishment

State Regulations

There shall be an Advisory Committee on

Judicial Ethics to issue advisory opinions to judges and justices of the

Unified Court System concerning issues related to ethical conduct, proper
execution of judicial duties, and possible conflicts between private interests
and official duties. Notes
